I am trying to install a six volt new fuel pump to my 55 thunderbird, replacing
the manually operated one. Where is the safest point to wire the positive lead
to without harming anything else? Thank you

</POST>



<POST>
<POSTER> coder </POSTER>
<POSTDATE> 2000-07-27T12:00:00 </POSTDATE>
Email: &quot;coder&quot;&lt;c ... @fbnet.net&gt;
