The best place to wire in the fuel pump is probably at the switch side of
the starter solenoid, but you should put a switch in between the pump and
whatever power supply lead that you decide to use. Also you might need to
consider speaking to the pump manufacturer about the possibility of putting
a fuse inline also. Just my personal opinion though! Rick Coder.
c ... @fbnet.net

